Articles.Content:
Are craft files of .90 compatible with 1.02? I can't get them to appear when I copy and paste them into my saved profile VAB folder. Any fix for this?

Thanks.

They should be compatible. There might be some that won't work (if it uses a part that had it's name changed, but I don't think that happened between 0.90 and 1.02) but even so those should still show up in the lists, just with a note saying invalid or locked part.
